author: rickhall
msg: Modified <ignorePackage> tag occur inside the <configuration> tag instead
of the <osgiManifest> tag, since this is more intuitive to me, i.e.,
configuration data goes in configuration while actual manifest entries
go in osgiManifest. Currently, it still accepts <ignorePackage> inside
<osgiManifest>, but it will issue a warning if used.

author: scheu
msg: Four tests plus the OMNamespace equals() code fix are contributed.
- a simple test for namespace access
- a simple test for prefix access.
- a test the pushes the corners on the equals implementation
- a test that makes sure that OMNamespace remains an immutable object.
